In prep for this talk, I checked the job pages of EA, Ubisoft,

22
00:01:35,038 --> 00:01:36,278
and Activision.

23
00:01:36,278 --> 00:01:39,820
And between those three, there are

24
00:01:39,820 --> 00:01:43,141
over 400 open tech art or tech art-related positions.

25
00:01:43,721 --> 00:01:46,122
And if you've been in any sort of position

26
00:01:46,122 --> 00:01:48,744
to hire a tech artist lately, you've

27
00:01:48,744 --> 00:01:50,585
probably seen this shortage firsthand.

28
00:01:50,585 --> 00:01:53,567
Two, it can be really lucrative.

29
00:01:53,567 --> 00:01:56,129
Tech art is obviously a technical skill,

30
00:01:56,129 --> 00:01:57,810
and you can charge like it.

31
00:01:57,810 --> 00:02:00,712
Now, when you're doing this part time, like I'm doing,

32
