you're probably not going to retire to the Caribbean.

33
00:02:03,393 --> 00:02:05,775
You're probably not going to buy a yacht.

34
00:02:05,775 --> 00:02:09,277
But you might be able to buy a car, or go on a vacation,

35
00:02:09,277 --> 00:02:10,418
pay off some student loans.

36
