And three, it can just be plain fun.

37
00:02:13,525 --> 00:02:16,787
You get to work with people you would never be able to.

38
00:02:16,787 --> 00:02:19,089
You get to work on really cool projects.

39
00:02:19,089 --> 00:02:21,651
You get to expand your skill set into areas

40
00:02:21,651 --> 00:02:24,613
that maybe your day job would never have you see.

41
00:02:24,613 --> 00:02:28,896
So let me show you some of my numbers

42
